{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Psalm 1 \uc1\u8211* The Way of Happiness

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 1}Happy are those
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who do not follow the counsel of the wicked,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
not halting in ways frequented by sinners,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
nor taking a seat in a gathering of scoffers.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}But the law of the {\scaps Lord} is their joy,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
they study it day and night.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}They are like trees
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
planted by runlets of water,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
yielding fruit in due season,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
leaves never fading.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
In all that they do, they prosper.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Not so fare the wicked, not so;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
like chaff are they, blown by the wind.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}So the wicked will not stand firm in the judgment,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
nor sinners appear, when the righteous are gathered.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}For the way of the righteous is dear to the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but the way of the wicked will end in ruin.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Psalm 2 \uc1\u8211* The Lord\uc1\u8217*s Chosen King

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 2}Why this turmoil of nations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
this futile plotting of peoples,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}with kings of the earth conspiring,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and rulers consulting together,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
against the {\scaps Lord} and against his anointed,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}to snap their bonds
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and fling their cords away?
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}He whose throne is in heaven laughs,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the {\scaps Lord} mocks them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Then he speaks to them in his wrath,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and in his hot anger confounds them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}\uc1\u8216*This my king is installed by me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
on Zion my holy mountain.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}I will tell of the {\scaps Lord}\uc1\u8217*s decree.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
He said to me: \uc1\u8216*You are my son,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
this day I became your father.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Only ask, and I make you the heir of the nations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and lord of the world to its utmost bounds.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}You will break them with sceptre of iron,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
shatter them like pottery.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}So now, you kings, be wise:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
be warned, you rulers of earth.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Serve the {\scaps Lord} in awe,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
kiss his feet with trembling,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}lest, angry, he hurl you to ruin;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
for soon will his fury blaze.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Happy all who take refuge in him.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Psalm 3 \uc1\u8211* A Morning Prayer for Protection

\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
{\i A psalm of David, when he fled from his son Absalom.}
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 3}How many, {\scaps Lord}, are my foes!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Those who rise up against me are many.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Many are those who say of me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
\uc1\u8216*There is no help for him in his God.\uc1\u8217* {\i Selah}
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}But you, {\scaps Lord}, are shield about me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my glory, who lifts up my head.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}When loudly I call to the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
from his holy hill he gives answer. {\i Selah}
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}I laid down and slept:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
now I wake, for the {\scaps Lord} sustains me.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}I fear not the myriads of people
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who beset me on every side.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Arise, {\scaps Lord}: save me, my God,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who strikes all my foes on the cheek,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and shatters the teeth of the wicked.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Victory belongs to the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
let your blessing descend on your people. {\i Selah}
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Psalm 4 \uc1\u8211* An Evening Prayer

\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
{\i For the leader, with stringed instruments. A psalm of David.}
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 4}Answer my cry,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
God, my defender.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Often from straits you have brought me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to spacious places.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
So now show me your favour
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and hear my prayer.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}How long, you proud people,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
will my honour be stained
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
by the slanders you love,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the lies that you follow? {\i Selah}
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}See! The {\scaps Lord} has shown me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
his wonderful kindness:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the {\scaps Lord} hears,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
when I call to him.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Sin not in your anger:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but speak in your heart
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
on your bed, and be still. {\i Selah}
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Offer true sacrifice,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
trust in the {\scaps Lord}.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}Many are longing
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
for fortune to smile.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Lift upon us
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the light of your face.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}You have put in my heart, {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
a deeper joy
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
than was theirs who had corn
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and wine in abundance.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}So in peace I will
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
lie down and sleep;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
for you, {\scaps Lord}, keep me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
safe.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Psalm 5 \uc1\u8211* A Prayer for Guidance

\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
{\i For the leader: A psalm of David, to be accompanied by the flute.}
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 5}Hear my words, {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
give heed to my whisper.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Attend to my loud cry for help,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my king and my God.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}When I pray to you, {\scaps Lord}, in the morning,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
hear my voice.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I make ready for you in the morning,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and look for a sign.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}For you are no God who takes pleasure in wickedness:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
