\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but the morning brings shouts of joy.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}When all went well, I imagined
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
that never should I be shaken.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}For by your favour, O {\scaps Lord},
\par}

