\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
but you hide your face,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and I was confounded.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Then to you, {\scaps Lord}, I cried,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
