\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Can it tell of your faithfulness?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}Hear, {\scaps Lord}, and show me your favour,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
{\scaps Lord} be a helper to me.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}You have turned my mourning to dancing;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my sackcloth you have unloosed,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and clothed me with joy:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}that unceasingly I should sing your praise,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
