{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
I trust in the {\scaps Lord}.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}I will rejoice and be glad in your love,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
