\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and cared for me in my distress.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}You have not given me into the enemy\uc1\u8217*s hand,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
you have set my feet in a spacious place.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}Be gracious to me, {\scaps Lord}, for I am distressed;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my eye is wasted away with sorrow.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}For my life is consumed with grief,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
