\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
My strength is broken with misery,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my bones waste away.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}The scorn of all my foes,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the butt of my neighbours am I,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
a terror to my acquaintance.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
At the sight of me in the street
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
people turn quickly away.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}I am clean forgotten like the dead,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
am become like a ruined vessel.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}I hear the whispers of many \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
terror on every side \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
scheming together against me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
plotting to take my life.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}But my trust is in you, {\scaps Lord}.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
\uc1\u8216*You are my God,\uc1\u8217* I say;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}my times are in your hand, save me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
