\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}Make your face to shine on your servant,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
save me in your love.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}Put me not, O {\scaps Lord}, to shame,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
for I have called upon you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Let the wicked be put to shame
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
silent in Sheol.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}Strike the false lips dumb,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
that speak proudly against the righteous
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
with haughtiness and contempt.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}How great is the goodness
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
