\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
you keep them safe in a bower
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
from the chiding of tongues.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}Blest be the {\scaps Lord}
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
for the wonderful love he has shown me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in time of distress.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}For I had said in panic,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
\uc1\u8216*I am driven clean out of your sight.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
But you heard my plea,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
when I cried to you for help.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}Love the {\scaps Lord}, all you faithful;
