\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}Let your hearts be courageous and strong,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
all you who wait on the {\scaps Lord}.
