{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Let the whole world honour the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
let all who live on earth be in awe.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}For at his word it came into being,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
at his command it stood forth.
