{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
we trust in his holy name.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}Let your kindness, O {\scaps Lord}, be upon us,
