The unrighteous will be destroyed forever,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the seed of the wicked will be cut off.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 29}But the land will belong to the righteous,
