\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}I acknowledge my guilt,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
I am anxious because of my sin:
