\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Hold not your peace at my tears.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
For I am but a guest of yours,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
