{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Happy the person who has put
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in the {\scaps Lord} their trust,
