\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
O {\scaps Lord} our God,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
your marvels and purposes for us \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
none may compare with you \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
were I to declare or to tell them,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
past counting are they.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}In offerings bloody or bloodless
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
