{\cf1\f1\fs22 7}This is what the Lord {\scaps God} showed me: he was forming a swarm of locusts, when the late spring grass began to come up after the king\uc1\u8217*s share had been harvested.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}And when they had finished devouring all the land\uc1\u8217*s vegetation, I said:
