How can Jacob survive,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
for he is so helpless?\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}The {\scaps Lord} relented. This will not happen,\uc1\u8217* said the {\scaps Lord}.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

