\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4} This is what he showed me: the Lord {\scaps God} was giving command to execute judgment by fire. It burned up the great deep, and had begun to devour the fields, and I said:
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}\uc1\u8216*Lord {\scaps God}, forgive, I beg you!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
How can Jacob survive,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
for he is so helpless?\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6} The {\scaps Lord} relented. \uc1\u8216*This will not happen either,\uc1\u8217* said the {\scaps Lord}.
