{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7} This is what the Lord {\scaps God} showed me: the Lord was standing beside a wall built with a plumb line, with a plumb line in his hand.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}And the {\scaps Lord} said to me,
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8216*What do you see, Amos?\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
And I answered,
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8216*A plumb line,\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
Then the Lord said,
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8216*Watch: I am setting a plumb line
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
