\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}Then Amaziah, chief priest of Bethel sent this message to King Jeroboam of Israel: \uc1\u8216*Amos has conspired against you right in the heart of Israel. The country cannot survive all his words.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Amos has said, \uc1\u8220*Jeroboam will die by the sword, and Israel will be led away captive out of their land.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*
