{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}And Amaziah said to Amos, \uc1\u8216*Leave, you who see visions, go to the land of Judah. Earn your bread there and prophesy there,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}but don\uc1\u8217*t prophesy any more at Bethel, for it is the king\uc1\u8217*s sanctuary, and it is the royal residence.\uc1\u8217*
