{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}\uc1\u8216*I am no prophet,\uc1\u8217* Amos answered Amaziah, \uc1\u8216*nor trained as one.  I am a shepherd and a keeper of sycamores fig trees.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}But the {\scaps Lord} took me away from following the flock, and the {\scaps Lord} said to me, \uc1\u8220*Go, prophesy to my people Israel.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}Now therefore listen to the {\scaps Lord}\uc1\u8217*s message:
\par}

