\uc1\u8220*You say not to prophesy against Israel,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
nor to preach against the house of Isaac.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}But the {\scaps Lord} says:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Your wife will become a prostitute in the city,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
your sons and your daughters will fall by the sword,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
your land will be divided up,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
you will die on unclean soil,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and Israel will be led away captive out of their land.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Time is Ripe

\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\cf1\f1\fs22 8}The Lord {\scaps God} showed me this: a basket of summer fruit.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}\uc1\u8216*What do you see, Amos?\uc1\u8217* he asked. I replied, \uc1\u8216*A basket of ripe summer fruit.\uc1\u8217* Then the {\scaps Lord} said to me:
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
The time is ripe for my people Israel,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will no longer overlook their crimes.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}The singing women in the palace will howl on that day,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
says the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Corpses everywhere,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
thrown out in silence.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Listen to this, you who trample on the needy,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
who oppress the poor of the earth,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}saying:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
When will the feast of the new moon be over
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
so that we may sell grain?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And the sabbath ended
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
so that we may offer wheat for sale?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Reducing the measure and increasing the price,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
cheating with false scales,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}mixing the sweepings in with the wheat.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Then we can buy the poor for money,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the needy for a pair of shoes.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Now the {\scaps Lord} has taken an oath
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
by the Pride of Jacob:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will never forget all their deeds!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Because of this won\uc1\u8217*t the land quake,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and all its inhabitants mourn?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Won\uc1\u8217*t the whole of it rise like the Nile,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
churn and subside like the Nile in Egypt?
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}On that day, says the Lord {\scaps God},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will make the sun set at noon
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and darken the earth in broad daylight.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}I will turn your feasts into mourning,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
all your songs into dirges.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will cause you to dress in sackcloth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
every head shaved.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will make you mourn like you have lost your only son,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
all that happens will end in bitterness.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}The day is coming, says the Lord {\scaps God},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
