{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
no one will escape.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}If they dig down to Sheol,
