{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and sinks like the Nile of Egypt.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}The one who builds in the heavens,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
who sets the dome of the sky over the earth,
