{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}To me, Israelites, you are
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
just like the Cushites,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
says the  {\scaps Lord}.
