I will destroy it from the face of the earth!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
But I will not completely destroy the house of Jacob,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
says the {\scaps Lord}.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}For behold I am about to give the command,
