{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 A Promise of Restoration

\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}On that day I will raise up the fallen house of David,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
