\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}So the {\scaps Lord} will only abandon Israel to its enemies
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
