\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Then the survivors will be reunited with their own people.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}And he will stand and shepherd by the strength of the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
In the exalted name of the {\scaps Lord} his God;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And they will live in security, for now he will be great,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
even to the ends of the earth.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}This will be our peace:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
when Assyria comes into our land
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
