{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
eight leaders of men.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}They will shepherd Assyria with a sword,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
