{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They will deliver us from Assyria,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
when they come into our land,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and tread within our borders.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}And the survivors of Jacob will be disbursed among the nations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
