{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like showers on the grass,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
which don\uc1\u8217*t wait for people to come
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
or linger for mortals.
