{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Israel\uc1\u8217*s False Conception of the Lord\uc1\u8217*s Character and Demands

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 6}Hear now what the {\scaps Lord} is saying:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Arise, present your complaint before the mountains,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
let the hills hear your voice!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Hear, mountains, the {\scaps Lord}\uc1\u8217*s accusation,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
listen, foundations of the earth.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
For the {\scaps Lord} has a case against his people.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
He has a dispute with Israel.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}\uc1\u8216*My people, what have I done to you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
How have I displeased you? Answer me!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}For I brought you up from the land of Egypt,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
from the land of slavery I redeemed you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I sent Moses, Aaron, and Miriam to lead you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}My people, what did Balak, king of Moab counsel?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And how did Balaam, the son of Beor, answer him?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Remember now the journey from Shittim to Gilgal,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
so that you might realise the just deeds of the {\scaps Lord}.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}With what should I come before the {\scaps Lord}?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Bow myself before the God on high?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Should I come before him with burnt-offerings,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
with calves a year old?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Will the {\scaps Lord} be pleased with thousands of rams,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
With ten thousand streams of oil?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Should I give him my firstborn son for my guilt,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the fruit of my body for the sin of my soul?
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}The {\scaps Lord} has told you what is good,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
