\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Only to do justice and love mercy,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and to walk humbly with your God.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Guilt and Punishment of Jerusalem

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}Listen! The {\scaps Lord} calls to the city!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Listen, tribe and assembly of the city!
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}\uc1\u8216*Can I forget the hoarded treasures in the houses of the wicked,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and the accursed scant measure?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Can I leave her unpunished because of evil scales,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and the bag of false weights?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}Whose rich people are full of violence,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
her inhabitants liars,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
whose tongues speak deceit?
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}\uc1\u8216*But I indeed, have begun to punish you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
