\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
because whatever you save I will give to the sword.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}You will sow but not reap.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
