{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
tread grapes but drink no wine!
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}\uc1\u8216*For you have followed the commands of Omri,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and all the practices of the house of Ahab.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
You have acted in accord with their counsels,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
so I will give you up to ruin,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the city\uc1\u8217*s inhabitants to derision.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
The nations will treat you with contempt!\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Utter Degeneracy of the People

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 7}Woe, woe is me, for I have become
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a field after harvest,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a vineyard after gathering;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
not a cluster of grapes to eat,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
not a fig that anyone desires.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}The honest have perished from the land,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
of the upright among people there is none.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
