\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They hunt one another with the net.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Their hands know well how to do evil,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the officer and judge demands a bribe,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the high official decides as he pleases
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and they conspire to pervert justice.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}The best of them are like a thorn thicket,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
