\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
The day of their punishment has come,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
now will be their confusion!
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Do not trust your neighbour,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
do not rely on a friend.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
From the wife who lies in your arms
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
guard your tongue.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}For son insults father,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
daughter rises up against mother,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
daughter-in-law against mother-in-law,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
