\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}He will tread under foot our iniquity;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
you will cast into the depths of the sea all our iniquities.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}You will show faithfulness to Jacob, and loving kindness to Abraham,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
as you have sworn to our ancestors from the days of old.
\par}
