{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}Now after the baptism of all the people, and when Jesus had been baptized and was still praying, the heavens opened,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}and the Holy Spirit came down on him in the form of a dove, and from the heavens came a voice \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8216*You are my dearly loved son; you bring me great joy.\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}When beginning his work, Jesus was about thirty years old. He was regarded as the son of Joseph, whose ancestors were \uc1\u8211*
