{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
{\cf1\f1\fs22 4}On returning from the Jordan, full of the Holy Spirit, Jesus was led by the power of the Spirit through the wilderness for forty days, tempted by the devil.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}All that time he ate nothing; and, when it was over, he became hungry.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}So the devil said to him, \uc1\u8216*If you are God\uc1\u8217*s Son, tell this stone to become a loaf of bread.\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}And Jesus answered him, \uc1\u8216*Scripture says \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*It is not on bread alone that a person is to live.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And the devil led Jesus up, and showing him in a single moment all the kingdoms of the earth, said to him,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}\uc1\u8216*I will give you all this power, and the splendour of them; for it has been given into my hands and I give it to whom I wish.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}If you worship me, it will all be yours.\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}And Jesus answered him, \uc1\u8216*Scripture says \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*You should worship the Lord your God, and worship him only.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}The devil next led him into Jerusalem, and, placing him on the parapet of the Temple, said, \uc1\u8216*If you are God\uc1\u8217*s Son throw yourself down from here,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}for scripture says \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*He will give his angels commands about you, to guard you safely,\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}And \uc1\u8220*On their hands they will lift you up, otherwise you might strike your foot against a stone.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}But Jesus answered him, \uc1\u8216*It is said \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*You must not tempt the Lord your God.\uc1\u8221*\uc1\u8217*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}When he had tried every kind of temptation, the devil left Jesus, until another opportunity.
