\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Blessed are you who weep now, for you will laugh.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}Blessed are you when people hate you,
