{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
for you have had your comforts in full.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}Alas for you who are sated now,
