{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*Father,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
may your name be held holy,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
your kingdom come.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Give us each day the bread that we will need;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
