{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}He was in the beginning with God;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}through him all things came into being,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and nothing came into being apart from him.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}That which came into being in him was life;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the life was the light of humanity;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}and the light shines in the darkness,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the darkness never overpowered it.
