\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}When the soldiers had crucified Jesus, they took his clothes and divided them into four shares \uc1\u8211* a share for each soldier \uc1\u8211* and they took the coat also. The coat had no seam, being woven in one piece from top to bottom.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}So they said to one another, \uc1\u8216*Do not let us tear it, but let us cast lots for it, to see who will have it.\uc1\u8217* This was in fulfilment of the words of scripture \uc1\u8211*
