\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 30}There were many other signs of his mission that Jesus gave in presence of the disciples, which are not recorded in this book;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 31}but these have been recorded so that you may believe that Jesus is the Christ, the Son of God \uc1\u8211* and that, through your belief in his name, you may have life.
\par}

