{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
from the tribe of Gad twelve thousand,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}from the tribe of Asher twelve thousand,
