{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}And all the angels were standing round the throne and the elders and the four creatures, and they prostrated themselves on their faces in front of the throne and worshiped God,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}saying \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
