{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}\uc1\u8220*My Lord,\uc1\u8221* I answered, \uc1\u8220*it is you who know.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
\uc1\u8220*These,\uc1\u8221* he said, \uc1\u8220*are they who come through the Great Persecution; they washed their robes white in the blood of the Lamb.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}And therefore it is that they are before the throne of God, and are serving him day and night in his Temple; and he who is seated on the throne will shelter them.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}Never again will they be hungry, never again will they be thirsty, nor will the sun smite them, nor any scorching heat;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}for the Lamb that stands in the space before the throne will be their shepherd, and will lead them to life-giving springs of water; and God will wipe away all tears from their eyes.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
