{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Then I saw what appeared to be a sea of glass mixed with fire; and, standing by this sea of glass, holding the harps of God, I saw those who had come victorious out of the conflict with the Beast and its image and the number that formed its name.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}They are singing the song of Moses, the servant of God, and the song of the Lamb \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*Great and marvellous are your deeds, Lord, our God, the Almighty. Righteous and true are your ways, eternal King.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Who will not honour and praise your name, Lord? You alone are holy! All nations will come and worship before you, for your judgments have become manifest.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

