\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Then the second angel emptied his bowl on the sea; and it turned to blood like the blood of a corpse, and every living thing died \uc1\u8211* everything in the sea.
