{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Then the third angel emptied his bowl on the rivers and springs of water; and it turned to blood.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And I heard the angel of the Waters saying \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*Righteous are you, you who is and who is, the Holy One, in inflicting this judgment;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}for men shed the blood of Christ\uc1\u8217*s people and of the prophets, and you have given them blood to drink. It is what they deserve.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}And I heard the response from the altar \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*Yes, Lord, our God, the Almighty, true and righteous are they judgments.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Then the fourth angel emptied his bowl on the sun; and he was permitted to scorch men with fire;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}and men were scorched by the intense heat. They blasphemed the name of God who controlled these curses, yet they did not repent and give him praise.
\par}

