{\cf1\f1\fs22 21}Then I saw new heavens and a new earth. The former heavens and the former earth had passed away; and the sea has ceased to be.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}And I saw the Holy City, Jerusalem, descending new out of heaven from God, like a bride adorned in readiness for her husband.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}And I heard a loud voice from the throne, which said \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*See! The tent of God is set up among people. God will live among them, and they will be his Peoples, and God himself will be among them,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}and he will wipe away all tears from their eyes. There will be no more death, nor will there be any more grief or crying or pain. The old order has passed away.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And he who was seated on the throne said \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*See, I make all things new!\uc1\u8221* And he said \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*Write this, for these words may be trusted and are true.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}And he said to me \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*They are fulfilled. I am the Alpha and the Omega, the beginning and the End. To those who thirst I will give of the spring of the water of life, freely.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Those who conquer will enter into possession of these things, and I will be their God, and they will be my children.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}But as for cowards, unbelievers, the degraded, murderers, the impure, sorcerers, idolaters, and all liars \uc1\u8211* their place will be in the burning lake of fire and sulphur. That is the Second Death.\uc1\u8221*
